WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.830
Good morning, family. How have you been

00:00:02.840 --> 00:00:05.710
doing? I just wanted to say hi today.

00:00:05.720 --> 00:00:07.470
I have some things on my heart

00:00:07.480 --> 00:00:10.669
to talk to you about.

00:00:10.679 --> 00:00:12.789
I've talked to you about angel

00:00:12.799 --> 00:00:15.110
visitations and things I have

00:00:15.120 --> 00:00:18.150
experienced with the Lord over the years,

00:00:18.160 --> 00:00:19.470
but I'm going to

00:00:19.480 --> 00:00:21.670
talk to you about some more of them. Some

00:00:21.670 --> 00:00:21.680
were

00:00:21.680 --> 00:00:24.870
angel visitations

00:00:24.870 --> 00:00:24.880
where

00:00:24.880 --> 00:00:27.150
I

00:00:27.150 --> 00:00:27.160
believe

00:00:27.160 --> 00:00:29.990
we

00:00:29.990 --> 00:00:30.000
entertained

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:32.749
angels unaware.

00:00:35.280 --> 00:00:37.069
My wife has had those

00:00:37.079 --> 00:00:40.190
experiences,

00:00:40.190 --> 00:00:40.200
too.

00:00:40.200 --> 00:00:41.790
First off,

00:00:41.800 --> 00:00:43.590
people wanted to know after the last

00:00:43.600 --> 00:00:46.350
video, "What

00:00:46.360 --> 00:00:47.910
do you do with the economy? What are you

00:00:47.920 --> 00:00:50.229
going to do with all that

00:00:50.229 --> 00:00:50.239
is

00:00:50.239 --> 00:00:52.150
going to

00:00:52.150 --> 00:00:52.160
happen?"I

00:00:52.160 --> 00:00:53.950
want to tell you:

00:00:53.950 --> 00:00:53.960
never

00:00:53.960 --> 00:00:57.869
be afraid. We are always to

00:00:57.879 --> 00:01:02.189
walk in victory. We go from glory to

00:01:02.199 --> 00:01:05.030
glory to glory. We're not afraid of

00:01:05.030 --> 00:01:05.040
anything—the

00:01:05.040 --> 00:01:08.429
economy, pestilence, or plagues.

00:01:08.439 --> 00:01:11.030
My

00:01:11.040 --> 00:01:13.630
recommendation is Psalm 91. Get Psalm 91 and

00:01:13.630 --> 00:01:13.640
Psalm

00:01:13.640 --> 00:01:17.109
23 deep inside your heart

00:01:17.119 --> 00:01:19.149
and meditate on that

00:01:19.159 --> 00:01:23.390
word. The Bible says

00:01:23.400 --> 00:01:24.910
that when David was talking, he said, "I've

00:01:24.920 --> 00:01:27.630
never seen the righteous forsaken or his

00:01:27.640 --> 00:01:30.749
seed begging bread."If He will take

00:01:30.759 --> 00:01:33.069
care of the sparrows

00:01:33.069 --> 00:01:33.079
and

00:01:33.079 --> 00:01:35.870
the animals of the

00:01:35.870 --> 00:01:35.880
woods—He

00:01:35.880 --> 00:01:37.630
takes care

00:01:37.640 --> 00:01:41.670
of it all: fish, flowers, whatever—God is

00:01:41.680 --> 00:01:44.109
merciful and takes care of His

00:01:44.119 --> 00:01:47.709
creation. We are His sons and

00:01:47.719 --> 00:01:50.389
daughters; how much more would

00:01:50.389 --> 00:01:50.399
He

00:01:50.399 --> 00:01:52.950
take care of

00:01:52.950 --> 00:01:52.960
you

00:01:52.960 --> 00:01:55.789
in these last days if you are

00:01:55.799 --> 00:01:59.230
a true child of the King? I'm not

00:01:59.240 --> 00:02:01.190
worried about any of this.

00:02:01.200 --> 00:02:02.830
People ask if I have

00:02:02.840 --> 00:02:05.230
anxiety about it—not at all.

00:02:05.240 --> 00:02:08.589
I tell you about it, but inside

00:02:08.599 --> 00:02:11.550
I say, "This is not for me.

00:02:11.560 --> 00:02:13.430
I'm not participating in

00:02:13.440 --> 00:02:16.509
an

00:02:16.519 --> 00:02:18.710
economic

00:02:18.710 --> 00:02:18.720
crisis."My

00:02:18.720 --> 00:02:21.630
wife

00:02:21.630 --> 00:02:21.640
and

00:02:21.640 --> 00:02:24.910
children

00:02:24.920 --> 00:02:29.150
will not do without. My Father

00:02:29.160 --> 00:02:32.350
owns the cattle on a thousand hills. He

00:02:32.360 --> 00:02:36.229
has it all in His hand. He is the God

00:02:36.239 --> 00:02:38.509
of the universe, the only God,

00:02:38.519 --> 00:02:40.509
the one true

00:02:40.519 --> 00:02:44.750
God, the Great I Am. If He

00:02:44.760 --> 00:02:48.070
dwells on the inside of

00:02:48.080 --> 00:02:50.869
you,

00:02:50.879 --> 00:02:52.869
He said He would never leave you

00:02:52.869 --> 00:02:52.879
nor

00:02:52.879 --> 00:02:55.790
forsake you. Lo,

00:02:55.790 --> 00:02:55.800
unto

00:02:55.800 --> 00:02:58.670
the end of the Earth, I will be with you

00:02:58.680 --> 00:03:01.949
always. If that is His promise to

00:03:04.319 --> 00:03:06.710
you, how much more

00:03:06.720 --> 00:03:08.750
will He take care of you? How much more will He provide food for you

00:03:08.750 --> 00:03:08.760
and

00:03:08.760 --> 00:03:11.670
your children? Even if the

00:03:11.680 --> 00:03:15.589
worst came and there was no food at all, He

00:03:15.589 --> 00:03:15.599
could

00:03:15.599 --> 00:03:19.190
bring the ravens

00:03:19.190 --> 00:03:19.200
or

00:03:19.200 --> 00:03:21.750
mana

00:03:21.760 --> 00:03:23.509
like He did for the children of

00:03:23.519 --> 00:03:26.110
Israel every morning. He

00:03:26.120 --> 00:03:28.470
brought them a cloud by

00:03:28.480 --> 00:03:30.750
day and a fire by night.

00:03:30.760 --> 00:03:32.869
That was under the

00:03:32.879 --> 00:03:34.750
Old Covenant,

00:03:34.760 --> 00:03:36.070
the

00:03:36.080 --> 00:03:38.030
Abrahamic Covenant.

00:03:39.680 --> 00:03:42.830
How much more does He have a

00:03:42.840 --> 00:03:45.390
covenant with you by His Son's blood?

00:03:45.400 --> 00:03:49.149
Jesus Christ

00:03:49.159 --> 00:03:53.550
died on the cross for you to be healthy,

00:03:53.560 --> 00:03:57.069
mentally sound, and wealthy. He became

00:03:57.079 --> 00:03:59.949
poor that you might be rich. He

00:03:59.959 --> 00:04:02.750
became sick that you might be healed.

00:04:02.760 --> 00:04:06.429
2 Timothy 1:7 says

00:04:06.439 --> 00:04:09.190
God has not given you a spirit of fear,

00:04:09.200 --> 00:04:12.110
but of power, love, and a

00:04:12.110 --> 00:04:12.120
sound

00:04:12.120 --> 00:04:14.670
mind. You don't have to

00:04:14.680 --> 00:04:17.229
have a tormented mind and fear every

00:04:17.239 --> 00:04:19.830
day because He's given you that mind of

00:04:19.840 --> 00:04:22.950
Christ. Jesus said,

00:04:22.960 --> 00:04:25.990
"Peace I leave with you, My peace I give

00:04:26.000 --> 00:04:29.510
to you."He already gave us His peace

00:04:29.510 --> 00:04:29.520
and

00:04:29.520 --> 00:04:31.510
comfort. So whenever

00:04:31.520 --> 00:04:33.629
you ask, "Brandon, how are you going to

00:04:33.639 --> 00:04:35.870
handle all this

00:04:35.870 --> 00:04:35.880
stuff?"stay

00:04:35.880 --> 00:04:39.110
in peace. Goodness

00:04:39.120 --> 00:04:43.710
and mercy will follow me all the days of

00:04:43.720 --> 00:04:46.909
my life, and I will dwell in the house of

00:04:46.919 --> 00:04:49.909
the Lord forever. Those are the

00:04:49.919 --> 00:04:51.710
promises He's given me; that's what

00:04:51.720 --> 00:04:52.950
I stand

00:04:52.960 --> 00:04:56.310
by. I see all this stuff coming,

00:04:56.310 --> 00:04:56.320
and

00:04:56.320 --> 00:04:57.670
when people ask when it's

00:05:01.080 --> 00:05:02.510
coming,

00:05:02.510 --> 00:05:02.520
I

00:05:02.520 --> 00:05:04.749
say this: I'll

00:05:04.759 --> 00:05:07.270
never go against another man of God.

00:05:10.150 --> 00:05:10.160
You

00:05:11.840 --> 00:05:13.550
might

00:05:17.240 --> 00:05:18.990
agree to

00:05:19.000 --> 00:05:20.710
disagree on

00:05:20.710 --> 00:05:20.720
timing—we

00:05:20.720 --> 00:05:23.309
all see

00:05:23.319 --> 00:05:25.629
in part—but I'm never going to

00:05:25.639 --> 00:05:27.830
talk bad about someone

00:05:27.830 --> 00:05:27.840
who

00:05:27.840 --> 00:05:30.270
loves the Lord. We just

00:05:30.270 --> 00:05:30.280
have

00:05:30.280 --> 00:05:33.070
different

00:05:37.560 --> 00:05:40.550
revelations.

00:05:44.319 --> 00:05:47.550
Let's be on the same team.

00:06:06.479 --> 00:06:09.070
We want to be winners,

00:06:09.080 --> 00:06:11.990
victors,

00:06:12.000 --> 00:06:14.390
and overcomers by the

00:06:14.400 --> 00:06:15.909
blood of the Lamb and the word of

00:06:15.909 --> 00:06:15.919
our

00:06:15.919 --> 00:06:17.749
testimony. That's what we set out to

00:06:17.759 --> 00:06:20.430
do: make the Rapture and stand

00:06:20.440 --> 00:06:22.589
before the Father and hear Him say,

00:06:22.599 --> 00:06:24.909
"Well done, thou good and faithful

00:06:24.919 --> 00:06:28.830
servant. Enter into my

00:06:33.430 --> 00:06:33.440
rest."Who

00:06:38.120 --> 00:06:40.070
gave the word first?

00:06:40.080 --> 00:06:42.230
Who

00:06:45.639 --> 00:06:48.430
cares?

00:06:50.360 --> 00:06:52.670
We're all

00:06:52.680 --> 00:06:55.150
hearing

00:06:55.160 --> 00:06:57.510
the same Holy Spirit. He speaks to

00:06:57.520 --> 00:07:00.309
each individual.

00:07:00.319 --> 00:07:03.869
The

00:07:03.879 --> 00:07:06.390
Lord

00:07:06.400 --> 00:07:08.350
isn't

00:07:08.360 --> 00:07:10.550
schizophrenic; He isn't talking to Chris or Pastor

00:07:10.550 --> 00:07:10.560
Steve differently

00:07:10.560 --> 00:07:12.830
than me.

00:07:14.639 --> 00:07:17.469
But

00:07:17.469 --> 00:07:17.479
how

00:07:17.479 --> 00:07:20.110
we interpret and filter it

00:07:27.039 --> 00:07:28.790
through

00:07:28.800 --> 00:07:31.990
our flesh is different.

00:07:31.990 --> 00:07:32.000
It

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:33.710
doesn't make

00:07:38.390 --> 00:07:38.400
anyone

00:07:42.800 --> 00:07:44.909
better or less; it just makes us

00:07:44.919 --> 00:07:47.230
human. We've got to

00:07:47.240 --> 00:07:49.790
walk in love.

00:07:51.800 --> 00:07:54.550
If

00:07:54.550 --> 00:07:54.560
I

00:07:54.560 --> 00:07:56.589
miss it,

00:08:03.479 --> 00:08:05.830
we walk in

00:08:05.840 --> 00:08:07.270
grace and love.

00:08:12.639 --> 00:08:14.430
We

00:08:14.440 --> 00:08:16.230
just keep picking ourselves up and

00:08:16.230 --> 00:08:16.240
trying

00:08:16.240 --> 00:08:18.790
harder next time. We

00:08:18.800 --> 00:08:21.110
seek His face daily.

00:08:21.120 --> 00:08:23.070
As

00:08:23.080 --> 00:08:24.869
my wife

00:08:26.400 --> 00:08:29.510
says, "I'm just a work in progress."That

00:08:29.510 --> 00:08:29.520
is a

00:08:29.520 --> 00:08:31.029
beautiful,

00:08:31.039 --> 00:08:32.790
humble thing to say

00:08:32.790 --> 00:08:32.800
because

00:08:32.800 --> 00:08:34.430
we're never perfect. Tomorrow,

00:08:34.430 --> 00:08:34.440
I'll still

00:08:34.440 --> 00:08:36.509
be a work

00:08:36.519 --> 00:08:38.430
in progress.

00:08:44.800 --> 00:08:47.670
Jesus is the

00:08:47.680 --> 00:08:49.829
only one who's perfect. No

00:08:49.839 --> 00:08:51.790
matter how well you think you hear Him,

00:08:54.160 --> 00:08:56.350
we're dealing with stinky flesh.

00:09:02.200 --> 00:09:04.269
The only way you're

00:09:04.279 --> 00:09:06.350
going to get good is by staying

00:09:06.350 --> 00:09:06.360
under

00:09:06.360 --> 00:09:09.030
Jesus'wings

00:09:09.040 --> 00:09:11.190
and saying, "Father, I need

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:13.150
You today just as much as I needed You

00:09:15.110 --> 00:09:15.120
yesterday."That's

00:09:19.040 --> 00:09:22.030
the only way we go from glory

00:09:22.040 --> 00:09:25.069
to glory. People ask

00:09:25.069 --> 00:09:25.079
why

00:09:25.079 --> 00:09:27.750
I'm

00:09:27.750 --> 00:09:27.760
not

00:09:27.760 --> 00:09:29.190
upset about

00:09:29.200 --> 00:09:31.069
the "doom and

00:09:31.069 --> 00:09:31.079
gloom."I'm

00:09:31.079 --> 00:09:34.150
here to warn you

00:09:34.150 --> 00:09:34.160
so

00:09:34.160 --> 00:09:36.190
we can pray and stop

00:09:36.200 --> 00:09:39.269
a lot

00:09:39.269 --> 00:09:39.279
of

00:09:39.279 --> 00:09:41.509
it, but because

00:09:41.519 --> 00:09:44.069
we are in the end times, things are

00:09:44.079 --> 00:09:47.710
going to happen.

00:09:47.720 --> 00:09:50.310
As labor

00:09:50.320 --> 00:09:53.590
pains upon a woman, so will it be.

00:09:53.600 --> 00:09:57.269
Labor pains don't

00:09:57.269 --> 00:09:57.279
pause;

00:09:57.279 --> 00:09:59.470
they

00:10:08.389 --> 00:10:08.399
increase

00:10:19.200 --> 00:10:21.870
until the baby is born.

00:10:33.120 --> 00:10:35.470
I anticipate things

00:10:35.470 --> 00:10:35.480
getting

00:10:35.480 --> 00:10:37.990
worse in 2025. By the

00:10:37.990 --> 00:10:38.000
end of 2024,

00:10:38.000 --> 00:10:40.550
we're

00:10:40.560 --> 00:10:44.269
going to

00:10:44.279 --> 00:10:46.949
have an escalation,

00:10:46.949 --> 00:10:46.959
and

00:10:46.959 --> 00:10:50.030
it

00:10:50.030 --> 00:10:50.040
will

00:10:50.040 --> 00:10:52.310
be even more

00:10:52.320 --> 00:10:55.150
intense in 2025

00:10:55.150 --> 00:10:55.160
and 2026.

00:10:55.160 --> 00:10:58.629
If anybody tells you

00:10:58.639 --> 00:11:00.670
things are going to get better in

00:11:02.839 --> 00:11:04.870
the world, they aren't reading their

00:11:04.880 --> 00:11:06.990
Bible. I'm not

00:11:11.839 --> 00:11:14.470
anticipating the

00:11:14.470 --> 00:11:14.480
world to

00:11:14.480 --> 00:11:16.350
get better,

00:11:16.350 --> 00:11:16.360
but

00:11:16.360 --> 00:11:19.030
I am anticipating a revival.

00:11:19.030 --> 00:11:19.040
I'm

00:11:19.040 --> 00:11:21.590
anticipating God's children

00:11:21.590 --> 00:11:21.600
being

00:11:21.600 --> 00:11:23.389
the head and not the tail.

00:11:31.360 --> 00:11:33.590
Every believer

00:11:33.590 --> 00:11:33.600
who

00:11:33.600 --> 00:11:35.389
presses into

00:11:35.399 --> 00:11:37.350
Jesus can walk in financial victory.

00:11:39.320 --> 00:11:41.910
Don't be discouraged.

00:11:47.279 --> 00:11:50.430
Jesus Christ is the same

00:11:50.440 --> 00:11:53.069
yesterday, today, and forever.

00:12:07.399 --> 00:12:10.590
I

00:12:23.199 --> 00:12:26.110
thank You, Lord, that

00:12:26.110 --> 00:12:26.120
even

00:12:26.120 --> 00:12:28.269
if there is no food in my

00:12:28.279 --> 00:12:30.790
cupboards,

00:12:30.800 --> 00:12:32.550
You

00:12:32.560 --> 00:12:34.550
are

00:12:34.560 --> 00:12:36.509
the God

00:12:36.519 --> 00:12:39.470
of more than enough and You will supply

00:12:39.480 --> 00:12:41.790
all my needs. I

00:12:41.790 --> 00:12:41.800
am

00:12:41.800 --> 00:12:45.189
a

00:12:45.199 --> 00:12:47.949
tither and a giver, and I have

00:12:51.279 --> 00:12:53.389
tithers'rights.

00:12:55.519 --> 00:12:58.350
He's provided for us time and time

00:12:58.360 --> 00:13:01.590
again. If

00:13:01.590 --> 00:13:01.600
you

00:13:01.600 --> 00:13:03.910
have

00:13:42.240 --> 00:13:45.829
a need, sow a seed

00:13:48.880 --> 00:13:50.230
in

00:13:50.240 --> 00:13:51.749
your local church or where you're

00:13:51.759 --> 00:13:54.829
getting fed spiritually.

00:14:01.639 --> 00:14:04.670
Give, and it shall be given

00:14:04.680 --> 00:14:07.350
unto you.

00:14:12.519 --> 00:14:15.550
The wealth of the sinner

00:14:15.560 --> 00:14:18.269
is laid up for the

00:14:18.279 --> 00:14:20.150
righteous. I

00:14:20.150 --> 00:14:20.160
say,

00:14:20.160 --> 00:14:21.710
"Devil, I'm taking it out of your

00:14:21.710 --> 00:14:21.720
economy."When

00:14:21.720 --> 00:14:24.509
a thief

00:14:27.639 --> 00:14:29.550
is

00:14:31.320 --> 00:14:33.949
found, he has to pay

00:14:33.959 --> 00:14:37.269
back sevenfold. You need to get so expensive that the

00:14:37.279 --> 00:14:39.550
devil thinks twice

00:14:39.550 --> 00:14:39.560
about messing

00:14:39.560 --> 00:14:42.230
with you.

00:14:42.230 --> 00:14:42.240
Stand on

00:14:42.240 --> 00:14:44.030
your covenant

00:14:44.030 --> 00:14:44.040
promises. Proverbs

00:14:44.040 --> 00:14:45.790
6:31 says

00:14:45.790 --> 00:14:45.800
he has

00:14:45.800 --> 00:14:48.310
to pay back sevenfold.

00:15:18.759 --> 00:15:21.430
We

00:15:21.440 --> 00:15:23.829
have

00:15:23.829 --> 00:15:23.839
tithers'rights

00:15:23.839 --> 00:15:26.350
to walk

00:15:26.360 --> 00:15:28.550
in

00:15:28.560 --> 00:15:31.910
abundance and

00:15:31.920 --> 00:15:33.990
an

00:15:34.000 --> 00:15:36.990
overflow harvest.

00:15:43.040 --> 00:15:44.749
Read

00:15:44.759 --> 00:15:48.670
Deuteronomy 28

00:15:48.670 --> 00:15:48.680
until

00:15:48.680 --> 00:15:50.910
it becomes

00:15:53.079 --> 00:15:57.150
real to

00:16:05.079 --> 00:16:07.990
you.

00:16:15.199 --> 00:16:17.749
Believe God for

00:16:17.759 --> 00:16:20.829
big. Believe Him for the impossible.

00:16:20.829 --> 00:16:20.839
I

00:16:20.839 --> 00:16:23.110
believe

00:16:51.040 --> 00:16:53.470
for

00:16:53.480 --> 00:16:56.269
supernatural

00:16:56.279 --> 00:16:58.590
increase, multiplication, and favor.

00:16:58.600 --> 00:17:01.230
Favor

00:17:01.240 --> 00:17:03.230
follows me around.

00:17:03.240 --> 00:17:06.350
I'm God's favorite kid. I

00:17:19.160 --> 00:17:20.909
even believe

00:17:20.919 --> 00:17:23.150
for parking places!

00:17:56.360 --> 00:17:58.870
We live by faith.

